age-quality-double-iso-d810-report/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2Fnikon-d850-image-quality-double-iso-d810-report%2F&d=L4AMZ6LbyX1Qs6BI5eXwoZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=69020d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petapixel.com/2017/08/24/nikon-d850-image-quality-double-iso-d810-report/</a>"},{"pid":"81bb16d78c79c4fbb3edf30389f7a7c17ece65c0","tid":373275,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64a286081bc43e0c643e731ceeb5c0d5131c379b","tid":373275,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:41:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Nikon also revealed to Imaging Resource that the new backside-illuminated (BSI) sensor design in the D850 &mdash; the first in a Nikon DSLR &mdash; isn&rsquo;t primarily for low-light performance but rather for speedier shooting speed by providing &ldquo;more flexibility in the chip&rsquo;s wiring.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nAnd if you&rsquo;ve been wondering about the origins of this new sensor, you&rsquo;ll be interested to know that Nikon designed it themselves rather than use an off-the-shelf sensor from a sensor manufacturer (e.g. Sony).<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;While Nikon contracts with a silicon foundry to actually manufacture the chips, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Nikon confirmed that the D850&rsquo;s sensor is entirely their own design</span></span>,&rdquo; Imaging Resource reports.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petapixel.com/2017/08/24/nikon-d850-image-quality-double-iso-d810-report/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2Fnikon-d850-image-quality-double-iso-d810-report%2F&d=L4AMZ6LbyX1Qs6BI5eXwoZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=69020d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petapixel.com/2017/08/24/nikon-d850-image-quality-double-iso-d810-report/</a></blockquote><br />\n而家講緊邊度生產"},{"pid":"24866dad449f2c4eb730b4f725c31da25e95a763","tid":373275,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"等睇拆機Sensor大揭秘"},{"pid":"f73697b43e36c11a26d66e2f7b1d1ffdcfd1883d","tid":373275,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>背照式 full frame 除左sony應該無乜廠可以大量生產？</blockquote><br />\nSAMSUNG<br />\n佢NX系列係BSI<br />\n不過啲機一直做得頹😫😫😫"},{"pid":"8c40bfc0d95422d88e6e9a8c4788a0ff2dc27ef1","tid":373275,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T08:36:41.000Z","msg":"留名睇人分唔同設計同生產"},{"pid":"90b284a30362f6fba7a8d186df1aa7a6112961f6","tid":373275,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇人分唔同設計同生產</blockquote><br />\n已經有人中左伏"},{"pid":"d3efb573e14c5ae9e14754d3c6403be9f7b09afb","tid":373275,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:44:58.000Z","msg":"其實點解d傳統光學大廠冇做sensor反而係sony做晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5bcb0974ba4cce0fc485881b927fcf9121bf22","tid":373275,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解d傳統光學大廠冇做sensor反而係sony做晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能當啲廠即用即棄<br />\nApple都唔會自己造CPU"},{"pid":"6176de4d4280ca6ba77bc424091c7b6db1be3c1f","tid":373275,"uid":67042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:55:22.000Z","msg":"可能係比leica個間cmosis"},{"pid":"80de791198f8637c8093762b9c2f9b18574de18e","tid":373275,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能係比leica個間cmosis</blockquote><br />\n願聞其詳"},{"pid":"16c45906a0e09cfb2651517e60ecc7d10c2f4393","tid":373275,"uid":67042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:58:46.000Z","m